Hello all,<P>May I start by saying Amen to Anum and Ravn.  Great posts.  We don't have a problem with the present Team Leader but lead where the masses want to go.  I am not saying you can get something fixed but you are our voice with Mythic.  Speak to the problems that concern most of us.  The pet problems and solo ability is at most a secondary concern. The game was built on an RVR Engine and I hate to say it boys and girls but Sorcerers suck RVR at present. Most 30+ Sorcerers are concerned with the following. <P>-Class Limitations with respect to RVR <P>-Lack a Mezzing Dominance as a Class<P>Point 1- Casting on an enemy rvr is great when you have to practically have to charge them to get within spell range.  What is the point when you know the tank are going to sprint at the fool caster that wanted to drop a nuke on them and crush them after your 1st spell lands.  Did they developers even take into account spell range with respect to an enemy sprinting at a caster? Endurance nothing a tank can easily kill a sorcerer without using styles.  It really fumes me when I see Theurgists and Wizards nuking away RVR when I still quite a ways out of range.<BR>Solution- We need longer range or heck I would love even 1 bolt type spell that can potentially hit from a range of more than 1500. Longer Range, Longer Range.<P>Point 2- Why would a group offer a spot to a sorcerer when a Smite Cleric can stun? It is more or less same result as mez, but a cleric can wear metal armor, has more hit points, and can heal (i.e. they are tougher than a sorcerer/don't die in 2 hits) Oh and can rez playered that died.<BR>Solution- I don't know but I am rather pissed that cleric's can do what our class was tailor made to do but with instant cast.<BR>As I see it, each class should have something they do best.  Healers/Cleric well they should heal the best no argument.  We should crowd control the best and right now I dont think that is the case.<P>In closing, I noticed Sillaf posted.  He and I being 2/3 of the all sorcerers 35+ on our server posting about the problems with this class says something. That is right.  On our server there are only 3 sorcerers 35+. Maybe 8 total over 30th level. Why would anyone play a sorcerer when it has so many problems.  Changes need to be made.<P>Lembolas Dazzlebolt<BR>Gawaine<P>--------------------<P>-Lembolas Dazzlebolt
