<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Sorry guys, this i the vocal minority syndrom at it's worst. <P>Do we have issues?  yes.<P>Do I bring them up, especially RvR? yes.<P>I fought tooth and nail against the reduced duration of our mez, and i am still fighting it as best i can. it was just a bad move all around. But may of the other items are just not what the MAJORITY of sorcerors seem to think. <P>In game many sorcerors group on many live servers. The sorceror still has the most crowd control tools available of any Albion class. There are server logs, and dev witnesses that refute MANY of the statements here. Stun is NO WAY near as useful as Mez as an opening spell, in PvP or PvE. Other classes are doign things with spells almost identical to ours that many here complain hey can't do.<P>Sorry, but the majority is not represented here.  <P>Now there are gret ideas here, and good feedback. I do NOT discuss items from Pendragon here, because then all i get is hearsay and opinion. Every time a sorceror posts their successes in PvP or in a good gorup, it immediately gets washed under by all the negative screams of how weak we are.<P>WE HAVE PROBLEMS!<P>But they are not the problems most here scream. The vault is MUCh worse. If a theurgist can do fine, with a lower pet, and less crowd control, how are we so damned gimped? easy, we aren't.<P>So based on hat he design team wants us to be, we need to fix the problems with what is not working and go from there. I am now getting direct feedback from he devs on issues like amnesia being broekn, if Charisma has ANY use whatsoever, how quickcast works, etc...<P>Things are now getting back on track after a huge launch. I don't expect them to be full swing till after the holidays. But they are coming in line.<P>So lets do what they ask, and fix what is wrong. THEN we can make suggestions for improvement.<P>and BTW..once again it is verified. Quick cast is indeed uninterruptable. If you can log one bing truly interrupted please post it or mail it to me, but as i have yet to see one the issue may b one of technique or hardware/lag issues.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...
